Privacy Policy for Bosaso Fast Food (BFF)
Last Updated: March 2026

This privacy policy describes how somdevops.net ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and shares your information when you use the Bosaso Fast Food (BFF) mobile application.

1. Data Collection
We collect the following personal and sensitive user data:

Personal Identifiers: Name, email address, and phone number provided during registration.

Order Details: Items purchased and delivery addresses.

Device Identifiers: IP address and device ID for security and app performance tracking.

2. Use of Data
Your data is used to provide the core service (food ordering), manage your account, and provide customer support. We do not sell your personal information.

3. Data Sharing & Third Parties
We share information with third parties only to facilitate services:

Payment Processors: To securely handle transactions.

Delivery Partners: To ensure your food reaches your location.

Analytics Providers: We may use tools (like Google Analytics for Firebase) to monitor app performance.

4. Security & Encryption
All data is transmitted securely via HTTPS/TLS encryption. We follow industry standards to protect your data against unauthorized access.

5. Account and Data Deletion
Users have the right to delete their data. You can request account deletion via the "Delete Account" button in the app profile or by emailing info@somdevops.net. Upon request, we will delete all personal data unless we are legally required to retain it for tax or regulatory purposes.

### Contact Us

For privacy concerns, contact us at: support@somdevops.net
